Symbol.Script_3D:
pen gs_cont_pen if gs_shadow=0 then shadow off
resol gs_resol
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end
material gs_frame_mat for i=1 to 4 extrude 3, -0.4*a/2, 0, zzyzx*0.65, 55, a/2, 0, 1, a/2-th/2, 0, 901, 0, 359.5, 4001 gosub 1000
addx 0.8*a/2 addz 0.2*zzyzx rotz -45 rotx 90 addz th*0.5 prism_ 2, a*0.48, 0, 0, 979, th/2*0.5, 360, 4079 del 5
rotz 90 next i del i-1
addz zzyzx*0.65 prism_ 3, th, 0, 0, 979, 0.7*a/2, 360, 4079, th/2*0.7, 360, 4079 gosub 10 addz th+th*0.35 gosub 10 del 1 addz -zzyzx*0.15 prism_ 2, zzyzx/2-1.25*th, 0, 0, 979, th/2*0.7, 360, 4079 gosub 1000
del 2 addz zzyzx-1.25*th gosub 10
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then material gs_seat_mat prism_ 2, 1.25*th, 0, 0, 979, a/2, 360, 4079 endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_DETAILED then hprism_ gs_seat_mat, gs_seat_mat, gs_seat_mat, gs_seat_mat, 2, 1.25*th, 0, 0.5*th, 1, 0, 0, 979, a/2, 360, 4079 endif
del 1
end
10: prism_ 3, -th*0.35, 0, 0, 979, 0.7*a/2/3, 360, 4079, th/2*0.7, 360, 4079 return
1000: roty 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
5000:
vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1
coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4
base
body -1
return
